{"tid":2092370,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都係熱血動畫，點解天元突破會係熱血動畫嘅天花板？","createTime":"2020-07-03T07:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T05:29:29.000Z","uid":321228,"like":39,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bfec1f05190bce96025abae3d697ce7803f5da","tid":2092370,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"1.熱血嘅定義係入面嘅角色，故事，音樂同加上自己嘅諗法從而&ldquo;令&rdquo;到你覺得熱血。<br />\n<br />\n2. 角色，故事同音樂&ldquo;叫&rdquo;你熱血就要即刻熱血。<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分熱血動畫都有（1）同少量（2）<br />\n<br />\n而天元突破就做到（1）同（2)，而且兩邊平衡。<br />\n<br />\n睇過天元嘅都知道，天元角色冇《海賊王》咁多曲線，故事冇《FA》咁有深度。整體嚟講，天元係一套非常正常嘅作品。<br />\n<br />\n但熱血方面我覺得冇嘢可以超越or同等天元突破。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅熱血就好似xx戰隊咁，你知道幾時會熱血同點樣熱血，但當佢&ldquo;叫&rdquo;你熱血，你仍然覺得熱血。<br />\n<br />\nThat's why 天元係天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167b246316355689664bb167ac11bb3fafe91835","tid":2092370,"uid":12186,"like":26,"dislike":40,"score":-14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"sor,勇者王同g gundam屌打"},{"pid":"d6221a619d3202257431d093880366384a8cf89e","tid":2092370,"uid":200529,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"感謝神魔令我認識依部神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2df2459df035b57710c4a0c1aa248d454800a89","tid":2092370,"uid":14087,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"因為大哥食左條女 自己永遠食唔撚到"},{"pid":"ab1fb0ba94a9a3b60dc578ea26c8ec4c5f2d2a04","tid":2092370,"uid":60527,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"167b246316355689664bb167ac11bb3fafe91835","tid":2092370,"uid":12186,"like":26,"dislike":40,"score":-14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"sor,勇者王同g gundam屌打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"勇者王final&gt;g gundam=天元&gt;勇者王"},{"pid":"8f5da1f1b68e8d201670cb5a87fb72553b0843e3","tid":2092370,